"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:9.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">9.2</span> 標題：烈酒、啤酒（strong drink, beer）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： סֹבֶא</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： sove’)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:22\">ISA 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:18\">HOS 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:10\">NAM 1:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： שֵׁכָר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： shekar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:9\">LEV 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:3\">NUM 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:3\">NUM 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:7\">NUM 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:26\">DEU 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:5\">DEU 29:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:4\">JDG 13:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:7\">JDG 13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:14\">JDG 13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:15\">1SA 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:13\">PSA 69:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:1\">PRO 20:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:4\">PRO 31:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:6\">PRO 31:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:11\">ISA 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:22\">ISA 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:9\">ISA 24:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:7\">ISA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:7\">ISA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:7\">ISA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:9\">ISA 29:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:12\">ISA 56:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:11\">MIC 2:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σίκερα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： sikera)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:15\">LUK 1:15</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>啤酒是一種能使人喝醉的穀物發酵飲料，通常比葡萄酒淡（即酒精度較低）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在許多語言中，烈酒都有一個統稱，比如「烈性飲料」。古代的人尚未發明蒸餾酒，如威士忌、杜松子酒（琴酒）、伏特加等。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:9\">LEV 10:9</a> ：<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 譯為“wine”（「葡萄酒」）的希伯來文詞語是指一種由葡萄做成的飲料；上下文表明，這種飲料可能經過發酵。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 把下一個希伯來文詞語譯為“strong drink”（「烈酒」），指一種由大麥發酵而成的飲料。在許多語言中，最常見的對等詞是「啤酒」。然而，這兩個詞一起使用時，代表所有含酒精的飲料。因此，「酒都不可喝」的禁令，所禁止的並不限於兩種酒，譯文應該清楚表明這是一般性的規定。如果目標語言有專門用詞來表示葡萄酒和啤酒，或者酒精度較高和較低的酒，翻譯者在這裡可以採用。如果難以找到兩個專門用詞，那麼也可以不使用兩個詞，而是譯成「所有致醉的飲料」。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:15\">LUK 1:15</a> ：希臘文<em>sikera</em> 可能是一個統稱，指一切能使人喝醉的酒精飲料。但是，這個詞在新約中只出現在此處，指用穀物做成的致醉飲料，與葡萄酒相對，可譯為「啤酒」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ）、「其他發酵飲料」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> ）、「所有其他含酒精的飲料」（如PV ）等。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
